{"title":"redis主从复制","date":"2018-12-28T06:11:00.000Z","link":"post/289","categories":["Redis"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:42:33.069Z","content":"<h3 id=\"1准备工作\">1准备工作<a href=\"post/289#1准备工作\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"三台虚拟机\">三台虚拟机<a href=\"post/289#三台虚拟机\"></a></h4><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/258874238.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"修改从服务器ip地址\">修改从服务器ip地址<a href=\"post/289#修改从服务器ip地址\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-enp33</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"重启网卡\">重启网卡<a href=\"post/289#重启网卡\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service network restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"三台主机ip：\">三台主机ip：<a href=\"post/289#三台主机ip：\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>192.168.1.8 主</li>\n<li>192.168.1.9 从1</li>\n<li>192.168.1.10 从2</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"复制redis文件\">复制redis文件<a href=\"post/289#复制redis文件\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">scp -r redis-3.0.0-rc2/ 192.168.1.9:/usr/local/</span><br><span class=\"line\">scp -r redis-3.0.0-rc2/ 192.168.1.10:/usr/local/</span><br><span class=\"line\">scp -r redis 192.168.1.9:/usr/local/</span><br><span class=\"line\">scp -r redis 192.168.1.10:/usr/local/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"配置从redis主服务器地址配置\">配置从redis主服务器地址配置<a href=\"post/289#配置从redis主服务器地址配置\"></a></h3><p><code>redis配置文件 /usr/local/redis/etc/redis/redis.conf</code><br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">slaveof 主服务器ip redis端口号(6379)</span><br><span class=\"line\">masterauth 主服务器密码(没有可不写)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"启动主从服务器redis\">启动主从服务器redis<a href=\"post/289#启动主从服务器redis\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/redis/bin/redis-server /usr/local/redis/etc/redis.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\">进入redis服务器</span><br><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/redis/bin/redis-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"常见错误\">常见错误<a href=\"post/289#常见错误\"></a></h3><p><code>master_link_status:down</code><br>需要关闭linux防火请 systemctl stop firewalld</p>\n","prev":{"title":"git回退到某个历史版本","link":"post/291"},"next":{"title":"JS 计算一个对象/Object的长度","link":"post/288"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/289/"}